Aremu Olaiwola Qudus (a mụrụ n'ụbọchị nke ịrị na atọ n'ọnwa Nọvemba n'afọ 1993; onye a maara dịka Director K na DK ) bụ onye nduzi vidio egwu Naịjirịa. Ya na ndị na-agu egwu nke ọtụtụ ụdị egwu gụnyere Wizkid, Skepta, Davido, Burna Boy na ọtụtụ ndị ọzọ a rụkọọla ọrụ, o meriri 2020 The Headies Award maka vidiyo egwu kacha mma nke afọ.
A mụrụ Aremu Olaiwola Qudus na 13 Nọvemba 1993, na Lagos Steeti, Naịjirịa
A mụrụ ya na Kwara Steeti n'ime ezinụlọ nwere ọtụtụ nwanyị
Ọ họọrọ ịga akwụkwọ na Creative Arts na Yaba College of Technology na Lagos.
Director K malitere ọrụ ya n'afọ 2015 mgbe ọ sere vidiyo egwu n'ihi ọchịchọ ịmata ihe na iPhone.
N'afọ 2018, Director K duziri vidiyo egwu maka Case site n'aka onye egwu Naịjirịa, Teni ma soro ya site na iduzi vidiyo egwu maka egwu Skiibii bụ Sensima
N'afọ 2019, ọ malitere ụlọ ọrụ mgbasa ozi na mmepụta ihe nke PriorGold Pictures nke na-elekwasị anya na vidiyo egwu, ihe ngosi okike, na telivishọn.

N'afọ 2020, Director K duziri Wonderful nke Burna Boy, na Suzannah nke Sauti Sol, nke mere ka ọ nweta nhọpụta abụọ nke Best Music Video na 2020 Afrimma Awards. Ọ gara n'ihu iduzi "1 Milli" nke Davido nke meriri Best Music video na 2020 The Headies Award
N'afọ 2021 Director K duziri egwu Grammy 'Essence' nke Wizkid gosipụtara Tems, abụ Afrịka mbụ e depụtara na Billboard Hot 100 na Billboard Global 200
